description.narrative: Supply is a key priority as CO has to meet regular requests from Government and partners for key emergency supplies such as critical hygiene and prevention items, including soap and buckets for hands washing, drinking water dispensers, disinfectant and personal protection equipment for use in schools (when these are not closed), health facilities, and public spaces. It also contributed in providing oxygen to health centers to fight COVID-19 and other diseases, based on previuous experience developed in 2019. These efforts were recognized by the Ministry of Health and national authorities. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:24/01/2022
